==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ongoing
<hw>On"go`ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of going
forward; progress; (<pluf>pl.</pluf>) affairs; business; current
events.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The common <qex>ongoings</qex> of this our commonplace world, and
everyday life.</q> <rj><qau>Prof. Wilson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>ongoing</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: ongoing
<hw>on"go`ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Occurring at
present; progressing; in progress; continuing; not <contr>past</contr>,
<contr>completed</contr>, or <contr>future</contr>; <as>as, an
<ex>ongoing</ex> petition drive; an <ex>ongoing</ex>
effort</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Onguent</ent>⟦br⟧
